      "description": "Shot Tracer ®  3D Map Tracer   Putt Reading   Golf Video Editor   Augmented Reality   Scorecard\n\nTrack your golf shots like on TV and turn every swing into stunning content. Shot Tracer ® is the ultimate golf tracer, ball flight tracker, and golf video editor, trusted by golfers worldwide and voted Best Golf App by Golf Digest and Golf Magazine.\n\nRelive your rounds on a database of 44,000+ 3D golf courses, improve your putting, and create professional-quality golf videos, all on your iPhone and iPad\n\nShot Tracer ®\n\nRealistic golf ball flight editor\nAnimate carry, distance, and shot shapes\nWorks on any course, no special hardware required\n\n3D Map Tracer & Course Flyovers\n\nBirds eye view of your shots on 45,000+ golf courses\nCreate hole flyovers and shot replays\nShowcase strategy and shot placement\n\nGolf Video Editor (NEW)\n\nCreate and edit pro-level golf videos directly on your iPhone and iPad\n\nBroadcast-style custom scoreboard editor\nVoice overlays with automatic captions\nAdd custom text, images, and graphics\nand much more!\n\nProfessional Scorecard Editor\n\nBuilt-in database with 44,000+ golf course scorecards worldwide\nDozens of pro animated scorecard designs ready in seconds\nFull customization with our new advanced scorecard animation editor\n\nAR Green Reading & Putt Line (NEW)\n\nBring broadcast LIV Line technology to your game.\nAugmented-reality green reading\nVisual putt lines to understand slope and break\nImprove putting confidence and green reading skills\n\nAR Tracer Fun Mode (NEW)\n\nCreate fun, engaging golf content with augmented reality.\n\nHit targets, hoops, and challenges\nShoot down UFOs in AR\nPerfect for creative social media clips\n\nMore Golf Tools\n\nDigital scorecard & scoreboard editor\n44 000 golf course scorecard database\nWorks on iPhone & iPad.Created by golfers for golfers.\nShot Tracer ® is a registered trademark of Visual Vertigo Software Technologies GmbH, registered with the USPTO and international trademark offices. All rights reserved.\n\nTerms of use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/",
